long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Shop RevMed is your browsing companion that effortlessly saves you money while you shop for medical supplies and equipment. Simply install the extension and continue browsing your existing providers. When you view a product that is available on RevMed, you will be notified with competitive prices on the same page.

* Search RevMed from anywhere
* Save money with secondary sourcing 
* Save time searching multiple sites
